Guess feedback

Computer generates code
 -4 colors
 -ordered
Human guesses code
 - ex. red, green, blue
Computer gives feedback
 - right color, right location
 - right color, wrong location
Human guesses again
Game ends when human gets the answer or 10 attempts have been made
Option to play again


